   1. Definitions.

      You cannot put buttons or animations in the LICENSE file.

You can add animated buttons:

On your portfolio website (using HTML/CSS/JSX) ✅

In your project's webpage (like index.html) ✅

In your README.md, but only simple image-style buttons (badges)—no real hover animations ❌

      ## 🔗 Features:-

- Stylish Animated Hover Buttons for better user interaction.
- Smooth transitions with scaling and shadow effects.
